## üõ†Ô∏è Technology Stack

|Technology|Purpose|Version|
|---|---|---|
|**HTML5**|Semantic markup|Latest|
|**CSS3**|Modern styling with variables|Latest|
|**Vanilla JavaScript**|No framework bloat|ES6+|
|**Font Awesome**|Professional icons|6.4.0|
|**Local Storage**|Data persistence|Browser API|
|**Netlify**|Hosting & CDN|Production|

### Why Vanilla JS?

‚úÖ **Zero Dependencies** - No npm, no build process  
‚úÖ **Lightning Fast** - Minimal bundle size  
‚úÖ **Easy to Customize** - No framework lock-in  
‚úÖ **Universal Compatibility** - Works everywhere  
‚úÖ **Perfect for Learning** - Clean, readable code

---

## üìñ How to Use

### 1. **Add Repairs to Cart**

- Click any repair item in the catalog
- Item automatically added to cart
- View real-time price updates

### 2. **Manage Customer Info**

- Enter customer name, phone, email
- Record device model being repaired
- Optional for walk-in customers

### 3. **Select Payment Method**

- Choose from Cash, Card, PayPal, or Crypto
- Cash payments show automatic change due
- Professional receipt generation

### 4. **Complete Transaction**

- Review order summary
- Enter payment amount (for cash)
- Click "Complete Sale"
- Transaction saved automatically

### 5. **View History**

- See recent transactions
- Track customer repairs
- Monitor business metrics

