## üì± Mobile Responsive

IFix U Pay is fully responsive and works beautifully on:

- **Desktop** (1920px+) - Full multi-column layout
- **Laptop** (1024px - 1920px) - Optimized workspace
- **Tablet** (768px - 1024px) - Touch-friendly interface
- **Mobile** (< 768px) - Single-column, easy navigation

Perfect for repair counters, on-the-go technicians, and home workshops!

